# bitnet.rs — BitNet b1.58 Inference Engine in Rust

[![Rust](https://img.shields.io/badge/rust-1.75%2B-orange.svg)](https://www.rust-lang.org)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
