    ///
    /// # Returns
    ///
    /// - `Ok(None)` for special tokens (ID ≥ 128,000) or tokens the tokeniser
    ///   cannot map to bytes.
    /// - `Ok(Some(bytes))` for a valid BPE token.
    ///
